'''Michel Vorm''' (born [[October 20]], [[1983]] in [[Nieuwegein]]) is a [[Netherlands|Dutch]] [[football (soccer)|footballer]], currently playing for [[F.C. Utrecht]]. his position is [[goalkeeper]].

He spent some time on loan at [[F.C. Den Bosch]].

In [[2006]] he was part of the [[Netherlands national football team|Netherlands]] squad that won the [[UEFA U-21 Championship 2006]] in [[Portugal]].

